## My Story

I'm a sardine tired of losing money when my liquidity pools go off range. And full-range pool fees are the worst.

So I thought — what if I could create a full-range pool but at the same time earn fees like a concentrated one?

And yes, PancakeSwap allows me to build this dream using hooks.

Hook Hogan replaces AMM bonding rules, changing the game completely.

---

## Features

All pools using Hook Hogan will have:

- **Oracle pricing** based on each token — highly resilient against MEV
- **Auto-setup fees** according to token categories and token volatility
- **Full range** — never worry about pool inactivity again
- **Auto-balanced inventory** — always holding more of the strongest token
- **Virtual concentration** — Hook Hogan makes your pool work as a super concentrated liquidity pool. More fees earned
- **Flexible deposits** — add tokens in any ratio

What does all this mean?

**Just set it and forget it.**

